<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="table/T5/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div></section><section class="tw xbox font-sm" id="T6"><h4 class="obj_head">Table 6.</h4>
<div class="caption p"><p id="P108">Distribution of types of errors in the second phase of auditing overlapping concepts</p></div>
<div class="tbl-box p" tabindex="0"><table class="content" frame="box" rules="all">
<thead><tr>
<th align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Error Type</th>
